      • Reagent

        public Reagent(int[] CASNo,
               java.lang.String Formula,
               java.lang.String Name,
               double Weight,
               double Stock)
        Initialize a reagent item.
        Parameters:
        CASNo - CAS Number of reagent, three segments of number in array int[]
        Formula - chemical formula of reagent
        Name - name of reagent
        Weight - molecular weight of reagent
        Stock - stock of reagent in lab, in gram

      • Reagent

        public Reagent(java.lang.String descript)
        Initialize a reagent item.
        Parameters:
        descript - a description string of the reagent. Each attribute should be separated by ":". For example
        141:78:6:C4H8O2:ethyl acetate:88.11:500.0
